Package sawfowl.regionguard.api.events

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RegionAPIPostEvent
    This interface is designed to access the plugin's API and check status.
    RegionAPIPostEvent.CompleteLoadRegions
    At this point, RegionGuard reports that the regions are loaded and provides information about the total number of loaded regions.
    RegionAPIPostEvent.PostAPI
    At this stage you can change some parameters that have no explicit connection to the game world.
